'''Smojmirovo''' ({{lang-mk|Смојмирово}}) is a village in the [[Berovo Municipality]] of [[Republic of Macedonia|Macedonia]].Smojmirovo's original name (with diacritics) is Smojmirovo. Smijmirovo's distance is 3.6 km/2.24 mi away from the center of the municipality.

